00021 ServiceTypeDef::ServiceTypeDef(QDomNode &serviceTypeNode): typeName_(QString()),
00022         typeDefinition_(QString()), parameters_(), constrained_(false),
00023         implicit_(false) {
00024 
00025         for (int i = 0; i < serviceTypeNode.childNodes().count(); ++i) {
00026                 QDomNode tempNode = serviceTypeNode.childNodes().at(i);
00027 
00028                 if (tempNode.nodeName() == QString("spirit:typeName")) {
00029                         typeName_ = tempNode.childNodes().at(0).nodeValue();
00030                         typeName_ = General::removeWhiteSpace(typeName_);
00031 
00032                         // get attributes
00033                         QDomNamedNodeMap attributeMap = tempNode.attributes();
00034                         QString tempAtt;
00035 
00036                         // get the constrained value as QString
00037                         tempAtt = attributeMap.namedItem(QString("spirit:constrained")).
00038                                         childNodes().at(0).nodeValue();
00039 
00040                         // convert the QString into boolean
00041                         constrained_ = General::str2Bool(tempAtt, false);
00042 
00043                         tempAtt = attributeMap.namedItem(QString("spirit:implicit")).
00044                                         childNodes().at(0).nodeValue();
00045 
00046                         implicit_ = General::str2Bool(tempAtt, false);
00047                 }
00048 
00049                 else if (tempNode.nodeName() == QString("spirit:typeDefinition")) {
00050                         typeDefinition_ = tempNode.childNodes().at(0).nodeValue();
00051                 }
00052 
00053                 else if (tempNode.nodeName() == QString("spirit:parameters")) {
00054 
00055                         // go through all parameters
00056                         for (int j = 0; j < tempNode.childNodes().count(); ++j) {
00057                                 QDomNode parameterNode = tempNode.childNodes().at(j);
00058                                 parameters_.append(QSharedPointer<Parameter>(
00059                                                 new Parameter(parameterNode)));
00060                         }
00061                 }
00062         }
00063 
00064         // if mandatory element is missing
00065         if (typeName_.isNull()) {
00066                 throw Parse_error(QObject::tr("Mandatory element spirit:typeName "
00067                                 "missing in spirit:serviceTypeDef"));
00068         }

00112 void ServiceTypeDef::write(QXmlStreamWriter& writer) {

00116                 throw Write_error(QObject::tr("mandatory element typeName missing in"

00118         }
00119         // if name was found write it + attributes for it
00120         else {
00121                 // start the spirit:typeName tag
00122                 writer.writeStartElement("spirit:typeName");
00123 
00124                 // write attributes for the element
00125                 writer.writeAttribute("spirit:constrained",

00128                                 General::bool2Str(implicit_));
00129 
00130                 // write the value of the element and close the tag
00131                 writer.writeCharacters(typeName_);
00132                 writer.writeEndElement(); // spirit:typeName
00133         }
00134 
00135         // if optional typeDefinition is specified
00136         if (!typeDefinition_.isEmpty()) {
00137                 writer.writeTextElement("spirit:typeDefinition",
00138                                 typeDefinition_);
00139         }
00140 
00141         // if any parameter are found
00142         if (parameters_.size() != 0) {
00143                 writer.writeStartElement("spirit:parameters");
00144 
00145                 // go through each parameter
00146                 for (int i = 0; i < parameters_.size(); ++i) {
00147                         parameters_.at(i)->write(writer);

00149                 writer.writeEndElement(); // spirit:parameters
00150         }
00151         writer.writeEndElement(); // spirit:serviceTypeDef
